org.softsmithy.lib.persistence

Class AbstractEntity

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.softsmithy.lib.persistence.AbstractEntity
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    @MappedSuperclass
public abstract class AbstractEntity
extends Object
implements Serializable
    A mapped base class for JPA entities with reasonable defaults:
    • A generated technical id (surrogate PK) of type Long with the generation strategy set to GenerationType.AUTO.
    • Since a PK should not change, there is no setter method for the id property.
    • Field access
    • implements Serializable
    Author:
    puce
